Package: FluxSeparator
Type: Package
Title: Separation of diffusive and ebullitive fluxes.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jonas Stage Sø
Maintainer: Jonas Stage Sø <Jonassoe@biology.sdu.dk>
Description: Separates the diffusive and ebullitive fluxes based on a running variance approach, as used in the scientific paper Sø et al., (2023).
  Aids the import of files from the DIY CH4 and CO2 sensors.
License: MIT License
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10), lubridate (>= 1.9.2), tidyverse (>= 2.0.0), TTR (>= 0.24.3), ggpubr (>= 0.6.0)
Imports: 
    lubridate
